          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-08-06T14:21:52Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Medicare Secondary Payer and Workers' Compensation Settlement Agreements Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill alters provisions relating to Medicare secondary payer rules with respect to workers' compensation settlement arrangements. Among other things, the bill provides that a Medicare set-aside fulfills secondary payer obligations if the set-aside is included in the arrangement and meets certain other criteria.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-06-18T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
